~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : ulog                                      ~FTPODnuts
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : ulog <user> [message]

   This allows an adphin to write a comment to a users ulog, or to read
   a users ulog. 
   the ulog is a per user log/history containing timestamped notes with 
   relevance to administration.

   Things that are automaticly logged to the ulog are : bans, unbans,
   arrests, unarrests, tags, untags and account requests. 

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   See also~RS : tag untag
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
